Package jsky.catalog.skycat.gui

Defines user interface classes for working with and searching in Skycat style catalogs.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
SkycatCatalogNavigator Used to navigate the catalog hierarchy.
SkycatCatalogNavigatorFrame Provides a top level window and menubar for the CatalogNavigator class.
SkycatCatalogQueryTool Displays a panel for entering query parameters and a table for displaying query results.
SkycatCatalogTree Used to display a hierarchy of catalogs.
SkycatCatalogTreeCellRenderer This local class is used to override the default tree node renderer and provide special catalog dependent icons.
SkycatPlotSymbol Represents the contents of a plot symbol definition, as defined in a skycat catalog config file.
SkycatSymbolConfig A user interface for setting plot symbol preferences.
SkycatSymbolConfigGUI  
SkycatTablePlotter Implements catalog table plotting for skycat style catalogs.
 

Package jsky.catalog.skycat.gui Description

Defines user interface classes for working with and searching in Skycat style catalogs. See the Skycat web page for more information about the catalog format and how to add new catalogs.
